id: pm-web-odwq
title: Implement 'pm web stop' command + pidfile-on-detach
description: "Extend --detach to write a pidfile (PM_WEB_STATE_DIR or OS tmp, keyed by port). pm web stop reads the pidfile/in-process handle, SIGTERMs the process, clears the pidfile. Graceful not_running + stale-pidfile cleanup. --json supported. pidfilePath unit-tested."
