close_reason: "Implemented. Verified end-to-end: PORT=... pm web --port 4555 --detach wrote pidfile (pm-web-4555.pid); pm web stop SIGTERMed PID 1816607, cleared the pidfile, server went down; second stop reports not_running gracefully."
